sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Caller
    participant API as OpenAI API
    C->>API: chat.completions.create\nstream=True\nstream_options include_usage=True
    loop Each SSE chunk
        API-->>C: chunk
        alt chunk.choices[0].delta.content exists
            C->>C: append to buffer\nprint(content, end='', flush=True)
        else Final chunk - no choices
            C->>C: cost = chunk.usage\nprompt_tokens + completion_tokens
        end
    end
    C->>C: return buffer + usage
